{"tid":773281,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[指點江山一人少一人]樂壇係咪靠依三個人撐住？","createTime":"2018-08-09T11:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T04:50:19.000Z","uid":20032,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"20a408bc17717c91d132cf6a772b45015eadd966","tid":773281,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T11:36:33.000Z","msg":"3. Post Malone<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/09/193055_aa644ea15d235069366184297a466c93.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2F193055_aa644ea15d235069366184297a466c93.png&h=ada92f39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPost Malone都可以話係一遇風雲變化龍嘅代表人物<br />\n積厚多年嘅氣運配合貴人相助令佢一舉成名天下知， 出嘅歌多次登頂傲視群雄，令佢穩坐釣魚台，當之無愧嘅第三名，pop教父"},{"pid":"079d2722fc4484c63bd5ea7f99c5b91978ec67e7","tid":773281,"uid":20032,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T11:42:46.000Z","msg":"2. Kendrick Lamar<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/09/193937_5f17c9198d2458bbed5663ac85c94cfc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2F193937_5f17c9198d2458bbed5663ac85c94cfc.png&h=79404609&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講完白人要講下黑人，我諗緊究竟講Ariana Grande 好定Kendrick Lamar好，但最後都選擇左Kendrick Lamar，無他，太偉大了。<br />\n如果話東方出左個夫子，萬世師表，出左個李白，詩聖<br />\n西方就出左個LeBron James，教育局長，出左個Kendrick Lamar ，饒舌詩人<br />\n夠偉大了吧"},{"pid":"5d3cf029da4e1a725ceed1043dceb6c3fbe6d045","tid":773281,"uid":37005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T11:43:53.000Z","msg":"以為你想講宇宙漿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad19d8e33b7c3d3b24704e6097d4f14120b9237","tid":773281,"uid":193951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T11:45:35.000Z","msg":"1.Offset<br />\n2.Quavo<br />\n3.Takeoff"},{"pid":"78a850df4fa9fdd34f95940d6e9071389226dc31","tid":773281,"uid":20032,"like":2,"dislike":